description: The ASUS Republic of Gamer (R.O.G.) series motherboard pioneers overclocking methods to enthusiasts. Maximus V Gene motherboard features Intel's Z77 chipset supporting the latest LGA 1155 3rd/2nd Generation processors along with DDR3 Dual-Channel Memory speeds up to 2666 MHz offer exceptional performance to gamers and enthusiasts. Extreme Engine Digi+ II technology is capable of achieving most precise adjustment, enhanced performance and stability, and O.C. capacity for CPU, RAM and iGPU due to highest quality Nichicon capacitors accommodating 5X longer lifetime usage and +20% improvement on the temperature. SLI and CrossfireX support enable fluid frame-rates at the highest game resolutions.
title: Asus MAXIMUS V GENE Z77 mATX DDR3 Intel LGA 1155 Motherboard
